Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.71,0:00:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you called me out of bed with this m...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.80,0:00:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the poster of headmaster Zefron go?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care for Zac Efron. Taylor Lautner is my man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.19,0:00:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, you [???] bitch?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.32,0:00:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Snape, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.35,0:00:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he knows where Dumbledore's\Nhiding and he's not telling me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.74,0:00:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's this stupid rule that won't\Nlet me discipline the children.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.01,0:00:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish there was some way\Nthat I could get my boyfriend...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.28,0:00:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...and kill Harry Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.58,0:00:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting that we kill a student?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.20,0:00:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not, Snape! That would be crazy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have crazy people running this school.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.53,0:00:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe if someone who also hated\NHarry Potter could kill him for me...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.63,0:01:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Look at ME!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.58,0:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucius Malfoy, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but overhear your conversation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.40,0:01:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to know if you were interested in\Na role in the evil scheme I've just choreographed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.19,0:01:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the part?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.53,0:01:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a meeting supporting villain role.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.80,0:01:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.52,0:01:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you want to find Dumbledore and have\Nunspeakable things happen to Harry Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.77,0:01:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can give you those things\Nfor a very small price.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.84,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,First you'll let my deatheaters into Hogwarts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our presence here must remain an absolute secret!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.28,0:01:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Next you'll lure Harry Potter\Nsome place where I can have him alone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.65,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be alone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is of the utmost importance.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.65,0:02:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have done this myself already, if he went anywhere\Nwithout that ginger and that filthy mudblood girlfriend of his.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. That takes care of Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about Dumbledore?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You say Potter knows where Dumbledore is hiding.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.70,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, before I finish him of, I'll use\Nevery torture imaginable to loosen his tongue.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.72,0:02:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And then I'll get my boyfriend Dumbledore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.30,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably out buying me presents. He's really sweet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna find and crush that criminal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.94,0:02:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... And once you have Dumbledore, Potter is mine!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, it's a deal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is all so illegal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.57,0:02:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone were to report this sort of business\Nto the ministry you'd both go to Azkaban!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.04,0:02:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why no one is gonna report it.\NRight, Snape...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.57,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, Severus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.40,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You better then anyone know\Nwhat kind of people the Potters are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Their arrogance knows no bounds!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.57,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something simply must be done about them\Nor there will always be guys like Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.60,0:03:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many douchebags in the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.06,0:03:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so many douchebags get the girls
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.49,0:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,who deserve more than absolutely anything
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.40,0:03:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that any charm or potion could ever bring.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.02,0:03:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But men like that, they have her on a string,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.55,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and they don't care,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.86,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For there will always be guys like Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.48,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To realize tears in your eyes because he got her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll never ever know how much you'd have brought her...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.19,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd only done
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,something more for the one,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.47,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,back when you were young...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sour grapes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Expelliarmus! Impedimenta!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So how did the exam go, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.73,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...butt trumpet?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilly Evans!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.31,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What has poor Severus ever done to you, Potter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.48,0:04:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's more the fact he exists,\Nif you know what I mean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.95,0:04:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're funny, James, but you're not!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just an arrogant, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...bullying...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...douchebag!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah,  I tell you what, Evans:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave Snape alone...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you go on a date with me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.59,0:04:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh, you're such an asshole!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so charming...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think I have a date then.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay.\N- We can hang out with my best friend, Sirius Black.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky Evans was here, weiner-jacket!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.63,0:05:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need help from a filthy little mudblood like her!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't help in the future.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, James!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.44,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.87,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So many assholes in this place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.55,0:05:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So many assholes in my face!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.51,0:05:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't they leave me alone--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.22,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To love princesses, maids, and queens?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.98,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't ever be in between...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.96,0:05:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd treat them nice and never be mean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.44,0:06:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And we would care...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.33,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But there will always be guys like Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.09,0:06:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'll quench the flame like it's a game with drops of water
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.32,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll never ever think her perfect as you/I thought her...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.65,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,... But now you're alone,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.38,0:06:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,left to pout and moan,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.11,0:06:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause you were totally pwnd.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do it!
